      span#resultstats.small.floatright Â 
section
  h3 Embedding Base64 content
  p You can embed the Base64 output into various documents using the following code:
  dl
    dt HTML embedded PNG image
    dd
      pre.language-html
        code.language-html
          | &lt;img alt="Base64 Image" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAADIA..." /&gt;
    dt HTML embedded CSS
    dd
      pre.language-html
        code.language-html
          | &lt;link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="data:text/css;base64,LyogKioqKiogVGVtcGxhdGUgKioq..." /&gt;
    dt HTML embedded JavaScript
    dd
      pre.language-html
        code.language-html
          | &lt;script type="text/javascript" src="data:text/javascript;base64,dmFyIHNjT2JqMSA9IG5ldyBzY3Jv..."&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
    dt CSS embedded PNG image
    dd
      pre.language-css
        code.language-css
          | .image {
          |   width:100px;
          |   height:100px;
          |   background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAADIA...);
          | }
    dt XML embedded PNG image
    dd
      pre.language-xml
        code.language-xml
          | &lt;image&gt;
          |   &lt;title&gt;Some Image&lt;/title&gt;
          |   &lt;link&gt;http://www.host.domain&lt;/link&gt;
          |   &lt;url&gt;data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAADIA...&lt;/url&gt;
          | &lt;/image&gt;
